## Project: 6 Notes App

A full-stack Notes Application built with the MERN stack. This app lets users create, edit, organize, and search notes.

## Features

1) Rich Text Notes (bold, italic, lists, etc.) using Quill.js

2) Categories / Tags to organize notes

3) Pin or Archive Notes for quick access and decluttering

4) Search Notes by title or content

5) Create, Edit, and Delete Notes easily

6) Responsive Design with TailwindCSS

## Tech Stack

Frontend: React.js, TailwindCSS, Quill.js

Backend: Node.js, Express.js

Database: MongoDB (via Mongoose)

## Setup Instructions

# Frontend

cd frontend

npm install

npm run dev

# Backend

cd backend

npm install

npm run